Jan 17 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several European companies, including Admiral, Blue Prism Group and Unilever, on Monday.


HIGHLIGHTS

* Admiral ADML.L: HSBC raises to hold from reduce

* Blue Prism Group Plc PRSMB.L: HSBC cuts to hold from buy

* Legrand LEGD.PA: Morgan Stanley cuts to equal-weight from overweight

* Sabadell SABE.MC: HSBC raises to buy from hold

* Unilever ULVR.L: Bernstein cuts to underperform from market-perform
